<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Orientation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">02.05.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introducing the students to the Department&apos;s faculty members, visiting the student application and research laboratory, introducing the university&apos;s library, information processing, laboratories, study rooms, common areas such as gymnasium, and ensuring the integration of students by teaching the rules of use. To familiarize students with scientific terminology by using popular topics in science.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 109</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General Biology I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.10.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Biology, Life&amp;Evolution, Scientific method, Origin of life, biogenesis, abiogenesis, The Chemistry of Life (Atoms&amp;Molecules, Water, Carbon), Carbohydrates, Protein Structure and Function, Lipids and the cell membrane, Nucleic Acids and the RNA World, The Cell, Introduction to Metabolism ( Metabolism&amp;Enzymes&amp;Control of Metabolism), Cellular Respiration, Photosynthesis, Cell-Cell interactions and cellular signaling, The Cell Cycle (Mitosis), Meiosis</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274017&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 111</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General Chemistry</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction: Substance and Measurement, Atoms, Molecules and Ions, Stoichiometry: Calculations with Chemical Formulas and Equations, Water Containing Reactions and Solution Stoichiometry, Thermochemistry, Electron Structures of Atoms, Periodic Properties of Elements, Fundamental Principles and Theories of Charcoal Bonds, Gases, Intermolecular Forces, Liquids and Solids, Properties of Solutions, Chemical Kinetics, Chemical Equilibrium, Acid-Base Equilibrium. Laboratory: Laboratory Orientation and Safety, Problem Sessions, Exp: Solubility Product, Exp Ball Viscometer, Exp: How An Element is Obtained from Its Oxide.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274018&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">TUR 101</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Turkish Language I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course covers the phenomenon of language, the main theories of the birth of languages, the characteristics and types of language.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274080&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ATA 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ataturk&apos;s Principles and History of Revolution II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Independence War, founding of the Turkish Grand National Assembly, international treaties, peace process, establishment of the Republic, Ataturk’s principles and revolutions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274089&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ENG 106</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English for Academic Purposes II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">23.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course covers the introduction to the research process, evaluation of information sources, avoiding plagiarism and APA referencing, reading and analyzing academic journal articles, preparing group presentations, using visual aids, and critical evaluation skills.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MAT 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mathematics II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This second course in calculus is based on the concepts of advanced integration, sequences, series and introductory level differential equations and vectors with the inclusion of their applications in various fields</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274101&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 110</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General Biology II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.10.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mendel and the gene, DNA synthesis and repair, The flow of genetic information: transcription, RNA processing and translation, Control of gene expression, The molecular revolution: Biotechnology and beyond, Diversification of life: Bacteria- Viruses-Fungi, Archaea and Protists-Protostome Animals and Deuterostome Animals-Plants, Animals systems, Evolution, Ecology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274095&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 112</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Organic Chemistry</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Teaching Methods: Slides, Exercises, Examples and Problems solving
Content: Structure and geometry of organic molecules, Alkanes, Stereoisomery of organic molecules, Alkenes and Alkynes, Electronic structure of organic compounds, Aromatic compounds, Reactions and mechanism, Alkyl halides, Determination of structures, Alcohols, phenols and ethers, Nomenclature, Aldehydes and ketones, Amines, Carboxylic acids and related derivatives, Carbohydrates, Aminoacids and proteins, Lipids and Nucleic acids.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274103&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">TUR 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Turkish Language II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes the types of written and oral expression the scientific research and citation process and topics to be considered in oral presentations.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274108&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Music Throughout History I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.01.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">A chronological presentation of what kind of art music is?</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274076&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 103</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition for Healthy Living</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.01.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This courseincludes the definition of nutrition and importance of food groups, macro nutrients, micro nutrients, water and drinks, the importance of nutrition in the Prevention of diseases, obesity, popular diets, eating disorders, diseases, nutrition, physical activity, and nutrition covers.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274069&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 104</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Science / History of World Science</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.01.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course examines the relationship between science and society with the development of Sciences since the beginning of humanity. In particular, the course will examine the change in the approach to science and the socialization of science since the first scientific endeavors. Science approach to change over time gaining autonomy of Sciences, the science-politics relationship between religion and science the relationship between technology and the Social Sciences, the development of the socialization of science, groundbreaking, paradigm-wrecker important scientific discoveries and theories of scientists the training and working methods, the relationship between science and culture are among the main topics of the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274004&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 105</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Story in Turkish Literature</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.09.2023</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic features of the story genre, the transformation of the story genre in the period from the Tanzimat period to the Republican period and the study of selected stories from Turkish literature.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274081&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
