<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular of Biology of Cells and Genomes; Cell Chemistry and Bioenergetics; DNA, Chromosomes, and Genomes; DNA Replication; How Cells Read the Genome: From DNA to Protein; the Shape, the Structure and the Function of Proteins; Control of Gene Expression: Transcription Factors and Posttranscriptional Controls; DNA Damage and Repair Mechanisms; Cellular and Molecular Biology Laboratory Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=274125&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
