<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">02.05.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Understanding PDB data, protein structure visualization, computational structure analyses, protein-protein interactions, molecular docking</Data></Cell>
