<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To think more creatively about civil society by more strongly considering the role of innovation in the context of various NGOs.</Data></Cell>
