<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Listening Skill: Culture
Listening Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to
• listen for specific information, main ideas and opinions
• identify main ideas and important details
• distinguish more important ideas from less important ones
• learn to use strategies to listen actively
• learn strategies to take clear notes
